title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 23 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 23 2021
description:
Senator Ted Cruz of Texas joins the program to talk about Biden's multiple catastrophes, mask mandates and playing poker with Clay in a celebrity tournament. Biden's policy on Afghanistan is a complete failure. The battle over mandates with freedom in the balance. The pushback has to come from the people. Our hearts go out to Tennessee flood victims.
